OL,3,CMoment Lexi Chambers completes 900-
OL,4,Cmile wheelchair challenge
OL,6,FA former NHS nurse and Army veteran
OL,7,Fhas travelled from John o'Groats to
OL,8,FLand's End in a standard wheelchair.
OL,10,FLexi Chambers, from Exeter, is a below-
OL,11,Fknee amputee who has multiple chronic
OL,12,Fpain conditions which have seen her
OL,13,Fundergo more than 20 surgeries.
OL,15,FBut despite challenges with her
OL,16,Fhealth, the athlete has achieved
OL,17,Fmultiple sporting accolades.
OL,19,FIn 2022, she broke world records for
OL,20,Fthe fastest half and full marathons
OL,21,Fusing a non-sport wheelchair.
