OL,6,FThe following year, she achieved new
OL,7,Fworld records for the furthest
OL,8,Fdistance covered in 12 hours using a
OL,9,Fwheelchair and for completing the Bath
OL,10,FHalf Marathon.
OL,12,FBut her latest challenge was perhaps
OL,13,Fthe toughest yet as she covered the
OL,14,Flength of the UK in a standard
OL,15,Fwheelchair.
OL,17,FLexi has travelled a total of 874
OL,18,Fmiles, taking on the equivalent to a
OL,19,Fmarathon every single day.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
