OL,3,CMoment Lexi Chambers completes 900-
OL,4,Cmile wheelchair challenge
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country
OL,7,Fafter crossing the finish line, Lexi
OL,8,Fsaid she was "amazed" at the support
OL,9,Fshe's received.
OL,11,F"I'm really, really overwhelmed," she
OL,12,Fsaid. "It's really hard to put into
OL,13,Fwords - I'm relieved, a bit tired, but
OL,14,Fjust amazed at the amount of support
OL,15,FI've had all the way through.
OL,17,F"The amount of people that are here
OL,18,Fright now is just massively
OL,19,Foverwhelming - it's wonderful."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
