OL,3,CMoment Lexi Chambers completes 900-
OL,4,Cmile wheelchair challenge
OL,6,FShe said the hills were the biggest
OL,7,Fchallenges - particularly when paired
OL,8,Fwith the recent wet weather.
OL,10,F"I didn't anticipate that many hills
OL,11,For how high they would be," she said.
OL,12,F"And then the hills with rain as well
OL,13,F- that can get pretty tough.
OL,15,F"I don't think there's a road in the
OL,16,Fcountry that exists that doesn't have
OL,17,Fa camber on it so you've got a hill
OL,18,Fand then the camber kind of goes
OL,19,Fsideways which means you've got to
OL,20,Fpush with one hand."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
