OL,6,F"I started with a ball from Exeter
OL,7,FChiefs women. I took it up to Scotland
OL,8,Fand then passed a signed ball from
OL,9,Fclub to club to club all the way down
OL,10,Fthe country to demonstrate the
OL,11,Fconnectivity behind women's rugby -
OL,12,Fand hopefully inspiring people to give
OL,13,Fthem a go.
OL,15,F"Go along to your club and support the
OL,16,Fwomen."
